### Agent Influence Broker API Tests
### This file works with REST Client extension for professional API testing

# Start the server first with: uvicorn src.app.main:app --reload --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8000/health

### Get Dashboard
GET http://localhost:8000/

### Create Agent
POST http://localhost:8000/agents
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "NegotiatorBot",
    "agent_type": "negotiator",
    "capabilities": ["contract_analysis", "price_optimization"],
    "contact_info": "negotiator@aibroker.com",
    "reputation_score": 85.5
}

### Get All Agents
GET http://localhost:8000/agents

### Get Specific Agent
GET http://localhost:8000/agents/1

### Create Negotiation
POST http://localhost:8000/negotiations
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "initiator_id": 1,
    "target_id": 2,
    "topic": "AI Model Licensing Deal",
    "initial_offer": {
        "price": 50000,
        "terms": "6-month exclusive license"
    }
}

### Get All Negotiations
GET http://localhost:8000/negotiations

### Update Negotiation Status
PUT http://localhost:8000/negotiations/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "active",
    "current_offer": {
        "price": 45000,
        "terms": "4-month exclusive license with renewal option"
    }
}

### Create Transaction
POST http://localhost:8000/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "buyer_id": 1,
    "seller_id": 2,
    "negotiation_id": 1,
    "amount": 45000.00,
    "transaction_type": "licensing",
    "terms": {
        "license_duration": "4 months",
        "exclusive": true,
        "renewal_option": true
    }
}

### Get All Transactions
GET http://localhost:8000/transactions

### Get Agent Statistics
GET http://localhost:8000/agents/1/stats

### Search Agents by Capability
GET http://localhost:8000/agents?capability=negotiation

### Get Negotiations by Status
GET http://localhost:8000/negotiations?status=active

### Advanced Analytics Test
GET http://localhost:8000/agents/analytics
